snippet.title: "Disney Pixel RPG" Official PV
snippet.description:
New Mobile Role-Playing Game featuring Disney Characters

Embark on a dreamlike journey, filled with unexpected encounters.
Head out on a unique adventure with pixel art versions of Disney characters!

- App Store(iOS) /Google Play Store(Android)
https://d-rpg.onelink.me/G8UD/ee1nsug4

- Official Site
https://d-rpg.com/en/

- Official Instagram
https://www.instagram.com/PixelRPG_official/

- Official Facebook Page
https://www.facebook.com/PixelRPGofficialpage

About "Disney Pixel RPG"
Genre:RPG 
Supported Device:Device compatible with iOS 17.0 or above Device compatible with Android™ OS 9.0 or above ※RAM: 4 GB or more 
Supported Languages:English, Japanese, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Korean, Chinese (Traditional) 
Scheduled Date of Release:In 2024 

*Information and gameplay images on this page reflect content still under development.
Actual game content at the time of release may differ.

© Disney.　Published by GungHo Online Entertainment, Inc.
